r\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-59357-433-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1-59357-433-9\">1-59357-433-9</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Effective+workplace+communication+%3A+skills+for+success+in+life+and+on+the+job&amp;rft.place=Indianapolis%2C+Ind.&amp;rft.edition=3rd&amp;rft.pub=JUST+Works&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=1-59357-433-9&amp;rft.aulast=Sudden&amp;rft.aufirst=Marsha&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+communication\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Whitaker, Steve; David Frolic; Owen Day-Jones (April 24\u201328, 1994). \"Informal workplace communication: what is it like and how might we support it?\". <i>CHI '94 Proceedings of the SIGHS conference on Human factors in computing systems: celebrating interdependence</i>: 131\u2013137.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=CHI+%2794+Proceedings+of+the+SIGHS+conference+on+Human+factors+in+computing+systems%3A+celebrating+interdependence&amp;rft.atitle=Informal+workplace+communication%3A+what+is+it+like+and+how+might+we+support+it%3F&amp;rft.pages=131-137&amp;rft.date=1994-04-24%2F1994-04-28&amp;rft.aulast=Whitaker&amp;rft.aufirst=Steve&amp;rft.au=David+Frolic&amp;rft.au=Owen+Day-Jones&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+communication\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Picardi, Richard P. (2001). <i>Skills of workplace communication&#160;: a han